title: Awww, the Woerdenwebers celebrated Eve's engagement on Gogglebox - here are Twitter's best reactions
text:
Friday, Oct 2 2015, 23:05 BST Share on Facebook Share on Twitter Share on Google+ It's that time of the week again - all our favourite TV families were back as Gogglebox continued on Channel 4 tonight (October 2).Twitter reacted as the Woerdenwebers celebrated Eve's engagement , while the lasses from Leeds are clearly still growing on fans… 
© Channel 4 / Jude Edginton Digital Spy rounds up the best Twitter reactions below: Literally can't even look at the screen when those two from Leeds come on #minging #gogglebox — Antonia Thompson (@ohhitsantonia) October 2, 2015 Already annoyed at those lasses from Leeds #Gogglebox
